  <brief_title>European Study of HF0220 in Mild to Moderate Alzheimer's Disease Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Safety/Tolerability of HF0220 and Its Effect on Biochemical Markers Relevant to Patients With a Diagnosis of Mild to Moderate Alzheimer' Disease</official_title>
