  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this Phase II study is to evaluate the safety and tolerability of HF 0220 in
      patients with Alzheimer's disease compared to placebo (inactive substance). The study will
      also validate biochemical markers as appropriate clinical end-points and to assess the
      suitability of chosen dose levels for future clinical studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
